# SDD — System Design Document — {{PROJECT_NAME}}

## Overview

{{PROJECT_NAME}} is a modular monolith: a single FastAPI process that exposes multiple independent products.
Each product can fail without affecting the others.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                  Browser / API Client                │
└──────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┘
