## Database

### Main tables
```
users               -- credits, active API plan
reports             -- validation results (no images stored)
api_keys            -- live/test keys per user and product
api_subscription_requests -- B2B plan requests
credit_packs        -- credit purchase history
admins              -- separate table for admin panel
```

### Convention
- Dev: SQLite at `./dev.db`
- Prod: PostgreSQL on Railway (`DATABASE_URL` variable)
- ORM: SQLAlchemy with `get_db()` dependency in each route

---

## Deployment

```
git push origin main
    │
    ▼ Railway detects push
    │
    ▼ nixpacks.toml: installs Python 3.11 + Node.js
    │  1. npm install && npm run build (frontend/build/)
    │  2. pip install -r requirements.txt
    │
    ▼ Procfile: uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port $PORT
```

---

## Architecture Decision Records

| ADR | Decision |
|---|---|
| ADR-001 | FastAPI over Flask (typing, async, auto OpenAPI) |
| ADR-002 | Modular monolith over microservices (small team) |
| ADR-003 | Firebase Auth over custom auth (don't reinvent the wheel) |
| ADR-004 | Reveniu over Stripe (native CLP support) |
| ADR-005 | Haiku precheck before Sonnet (cost proportional to risk) |
